Text: RE Christmas Party Cc PST Damn I planned on going until I saw the invite list Just kidding it will be good to see you all again even Benson Mark Original Message From Benson Goebel SMTP Sent TuesdayDecember AM To Cc StaceyW NRONcom Subject Christmas Party Kendrich wanted me to let everyone know that he is having a Christmas Party at his parents house in Cuero It is set for Sunday December at around pm Please spread the word Snacks and Appetizers will be provided BYOB Benson
